---
title: "US45 — Create / manage expert profile"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Expert User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>ExpertProfileScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>UpdateExpertProfile
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>ExpertProfile
  A->>B: edit bio, credentials, photo, tap SAVE
  B->>C: save(profile)
  C->>E: saveExpertProfile(profile)
  alt saved
    E-->>C: ExpertProfile (updated)
    C-->>B: state = AsyncData (saved)
    B-->>A: public profile updated
  else save failed
    E-->>C: PostgrestException
    C-->>B: state = AsyncError
    B-->>A: "Could not save profile. Try again."
  end
  note over E: saveExpertProfile via SupabaseGateway → expert_profiles (RLS)
